comments: Williams (DAL) attempts to tie the ball up as he reaches in and initiates arm contact with Allen (CLE) that affects his ability to control the ball.
LeVert (CLE) firms up over his left foot as he establishes himself in Jones Jr.'s (DAL) path and absorbs the body contact during Jones Jr.'s driving shot attempt.
Doncic (DAL) maintains verticality and absorbs the contact that occurs during LeVert's (CLE) driving shot attempt.
LeVert (CLE) is moving alongside Doncic's (DAL) path and marginal body contact occurs as the two come together during the drive.
Doncic (DAL) steps to, not through LeVert's (CLE) space and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the shot attempt near the rim.
Doncic (DAL) makes clean contact with the ball as he contests LeVert's (CLE) jump shot prior to any incidental wrist contact that occurs.
Allen (CLE) does not maintain a legal guarding position as he moves into Doncic's (DAL) body, initiating arm and body contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
Exum (DAL) commits a take foul on Okoro (CLE).
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) commits a take foul on LeVert (CLE).
Doncic (DAL) and LeVert (CLE) come together, and marginal contact occurs as Doncic releases away on the perimeter.
Lively II (DAL) commits a take foul on Niang (CLE).
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) avoids stepping out of bounds while still in possession of the ball.
Strus (CLE) makes clean contact with the ball as he legally contests Curry's (DAL) jump shot attempt.
